{"tid":153182,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"不甘愛隊出局被寸　PSG球迷殺抽水朋友","createTime":"2017-03-12T11:32:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-12T12:01:51.000Z","uid":20473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"326515906f7210c1ef5c51067c1a576fdd710eea","tid":153182,"uid":20473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T11:32:53.000Z","msg":"不甘愛隊出局被寸　PSG球迷殺抽水朋友<br />\n<br />\n在剛完成的歐聯16強次回合賽事，最經典的比賽首推巴塞隆拿以6:1大炒巴黎聖日耳門（PSG），兩回合計以6:5反勝對手，驚險晉級。 相信不少PSG球迷，都對出局感到不是味兒，特別是被揶揄的時候。一名在非洲加蓬的18歲PSG球迷，就因為不甘愛隊被朋友嘲笑而出手。 該名PSG球迷，於星期三賽後與友人飲酒消遣，期間有朋友不斷抽水，嘲笑PSG出局，令酒醉的他非常憤怒，他一怒之下，竟然襲擊對方的頸部，令對方當場死亡。 該名PSG球迷當場被捕，他承認出手，但強調無意將對方置於死地。<br />\n<br />\n- 熱血時報網站連結 <a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/03-11-2017/36506\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F03-11-2017%2F36506&d=TzvjPMdTsSggZCZjY4uR20%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=5dac5568\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/03-11-2017/36506</a><br />\n- Copyright &copy; 2017"},{"pid":"b384c44084e77dec72417afe31aa6e6f02f76e77","tid":153182,"uid":1289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T11:34:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"def36aabd9e4c06e341d9b2de3f2b52698c5730d","tid":153182,"uid":57035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T11:35:14.000Z","msg":"等睇有ching話真男人"},{"pid":"77246ac0c0a31de2b64c31d5173feb0f945afed7","tid":153182,"uid":20473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T12:01:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}